Package: fancy-tar
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash, pv, gnu-tar, coreutils, p7zip-full
Recommends: gpg, openssl
Description: Smart archive tool with progress bars and encryption
 fancy-tar is a smarter, friendlier tar tool with progress bars, tree views,
 encryption, ZIP support, and more. It supports creating .tar, .tar.gz, .zip,
 and .7z archives with optional encryption using GPG, OpenSSL, or 7z's built-in
 AES-256 encryption.
 .
 Features include:
  * Progress bars for archive operations
  * Tree-style file previews
  * Multiple encryption options
  * Secure password handling
  * SHA256 checksum generation
  * Split archive support
  * Archive verification 